   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Maimachos to Zenon, greetings. If you are well, and other things are satisfactory, you do well and I give thanks to the gods. I am myself also well... [Remaining part of the preserved text is too fragmentary for translation].";(Verso): "Year 37, Hathyr 17. Maimachos."</ab>
